snippet.title: Brawlhalla Cinematic Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Brawlhalla is free to play with full cross-play for Playstation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, Steam, iOS, and Android!
Get it here: https://www.brawlhalla.com/play
